import React from 'react' import './dashboard.css' import { Fragment } from 'react' import NAV from '../components/nav' import { isauthenticated } from '../auth/authenticate' function DASHBOARD() { const user=isauthenticated() console.log(user.user.isadmin) return (
  • Username is {user.user.username}
  • Email is {user.user.email}
  • isadmin {user.user.isadmin ? "true" :"False"}
  • {user.user.isadmin ? go to admin page :Edit you profile}
) } export default DASHBOARD
